entries.journal_entry_description: Bring Cal Handro in to Wolff Kalos.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the safehouse and talk to the head guard.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have been attacked by mercenaries, hired by the Imperials.  Kill them before they kill you!
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Now that you survived the attack, talk to the Head Guard again.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Talk to the Head Guard Again
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: It seems that Officer M'Kae was also interested in acquiring Cal.  Get information from him one way or another.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: You know where Cal Handro is. Go into space and shoot him down before he can further damage the Alliance.  Return to Wolff Kalos when you have won.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: You have been rewarded for a job well done.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return to Wolff Kalos and learn if there is something that you can do about Officer M'Kae.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Kill General Brant Korra and acquire his computer codes
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Use the main computer terminal to download Officer M'Kae's journal.
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: Return to Officer M'Kae and encourage him to cooperate.
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: You know where Cal Handro is. Go into space and shoot him down before he can further damage the Alliance.  Return to Wolff Kalos when you have won.
entries.task14_journal_entry_description: You have been rewarded for a job well done.
